---
layout: post
title: "{{ title }}"
subtitle: "{{ one_line_summary | replace('"', "'") }}"
summary: "{{ one_line_summary | replace('"', "'") }}"
date: "{{ date }}"
slug: "{{ slug }}"
paper: true
categories: papers
tags:
  - paper
  - arxiv
  - summary
image: "{{ '/' ~ image if image else '' }}"
source_pdf: "{{ source_pdf }}"
source_url: "{{ source_url }}"
pdf_url: "{{ pdf_url }}"
arxiv_id: "{{ arxiv_id }}"
license: "{{ license }}"
model: "{{ model_name }}"
model_path: "{{ model_path }}"
backend: "{{ backend }}"
review_status: "{{ review_status }}"
featured_overview_image: "{{ '/' ~ featured_visuals[0].rel_path if featured_visuals else '' }}"
featured_table_image: "{{ '/' ~ featured_visuals[1].rel_path if featured_visuals|length > 1 else '' }}"
---

# {{ title }}

> {{ one_line_summary }}

## 오버뷰

{% if featured_visuals %}
<div class="paper-spotlight-grid">
{% for visual in featured_visuals %}
  <figure class="paper-spotlight-card">
    <img src="{{ '/' ~ visual.rel_path }}" alt="{{ visual.alt }}">
    <figcaption>
      <strong>{{ visual.title }}</strong>
      <span class="paper-caption">{{ visual.caption or visual.alt }}</span>
      {% if visual.selection_reason %}
      <span class="paper-reason">선정 이유: {{ visual.selection_reason }}</span>
      {% endif %}
      {% if visual.source_note %}
      <span class="paper-source">출처: {{ visual.source_note }}</span>
      {% endif %}
    </figcaption>
  </figure>
{% endfor %}
</div>
{% else %}
대표 오버뷰 피규어와 메인 실험 테이블이 아직 선택되지 않았다.
{% endif %}

## 핵심 주장

{% if key_claim_lines %}
{{ key_claim_lines }}
{% else %}
- 핵심 주장 추출에 실패했다.
{% endif %}

## 초록
{{ sections[0].body if sections and sections[0].title == '초록' else one_line_summary }}

{% for section in sections %}
{% if section.title != '초록' %}
## {{ section.title }}
{{ section.body }}

{% if section.bullets %}
{% for bullet in section.bullets %}
- {{ bullet }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if figures %}
## 그림 전체
<div class="figure-grid">
{% for figure in figures %}
  <figure class="figure-card">
    <img src="{{ '/' ~ figure.rel_path }}" alt="{{ figure.alt }}">
    <figcaption>
      <strong>Figure {{ figure.index }}</strong>
      <span class="paper-caption">{{ figure.caption or figure.alt }}</span>
      {% if figure.source_note %}
      <span class="paper-source">출처: {{ figure.source_note }}</span>
      {% endif %}
    </figcaption>
  </figure>
{% endfor %}
</div>
{% endif %}

## 검수 로그
<div class="verification-box">
<strong>1차 팩트체크</strong>: {{ review_pass_1.status }}
{% if review_pass_1.findings %}
<ul>
{% for finding in review_pass_1.findings %}
  <li>{{ finding }}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
{% else %}
- 통과
{% endif %}

<strong>2차 팩트체크</strong>: {{ review_pass_2.status }}
{% if review_pass_2.findings %}
<ul>
{% for finding in review_pass_2.findings %}
  <li>{{ finding }}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
{% else %}
- 통과
{% endif %}
</div>

## 출처
- 원문 PDF: {{ source_pdf }}
- 논문 페이지: {{ source_url }}
- PDF URL: {{ pdf_url }}
- 라이선스: {{ license }}
- 모델: {{ model_name }}
- 백엔드: {{ backend }}
